  <description type="morphology">Plants 20–60 cm. Leaves moderately crowded, green; blades 1-nerved, linear, 20–40 × ca. 1 mm, faces glabrous or sparsely hairy, eglandular, somewhat viscid; distalmost shorter than arrays. Heads 5–10 in compact, racemiform arrays. Involucres 11–12.5 mm. Phyllaries 13–22, apices erect, attenuate. Florets 5–7; corollas clear yellow, 10–11 mm, tubes glabrous, throats gradually dilated, lobes 1.5–2 mm. 2n = 18.</description>
